  <brief_title>Preference of Genetic Polymorphism and Pharmacokinetics</brief_title>
  <official_title>Preference of CYP450 2B6 516 G&gt;T Polymorphism and Pharmacokinetics of Plasma Efavirenz in A Group of HIV Infected Southern Chinese</official_title>
